    "body": "@seanchas116 I'm just trying to understand how to use this in my app. I load an HTML file from a local HTTP server with Electron, and I would like to require my modules relative to the index.html file that I load. Will this help me achieve that? So far with my experimenting it doesn't seem to help, the app root is set to some strange location in node_modules/electron/bla/bla, which doesn't help get to any of the node_modules that my application would actually use. Any insight would be appreciated"
